      right: ["Rapidly growing, ulcerated, or bleeding melanoma lesion","Multiple satellite or in-transit metastases","Bulky, fixed, or matted regional lymphadenopathy","Neurological symptoms suggesting brain metastasis (headache, seizure, focal deficits)","Immune-related adverse events from immunotherapy (severe colitis, hepatitis, pneumonitis, adrenal crisis)"]
