      type: "Progestogen — synthetic progestin",
      action: "Opposes estrogen-stimulated endometrial proliferation, preventing endometrial hyperplasia and carcinoma when combined with estrogen therapy in women with an intact uterus",
      sideEffects: "Bloating, mood changes, breast tenderness, headache, irregular bleeding during initial months",
      contra: "Known or suspected breast cancer, active liver disease, undiagnosed vaginal bleeding, history of VTE",
